    <description>This flow is used to update the snapshot Advice Recommendations field when an advice record is moved to &quot;Await Decision&quot; (at which point all recommendations/fulfilment should have been added to the advice).</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <interviewLabel>Advice | Update snapshot with recommendations {!$Flow.CurrentDateTime}</interviewLabel>
